    <note>Liu(2) Ren [16620] He was Han Gaozu's grandfather and the first Pengcheng Liu(2), although Liu(2) Yizhi [3594], in his funerary inscription for his uncle, Gong [3597], identifies the "real" Pengcheng Liu(2) as beginning with the enfeoffment of Han Xuandi's son. However, the Pengcheng Liu(2) rulers of Liu(2) Song trace their ancestry to Liu(2) Bang's [16622] younger brother, Jiao(2) [12171]. I will use Ren as the penultimate ancestor for all Pengcheng Liu w/o detailed lineage information. See XTS, 71A.26b-27a.</note>
